<pb facs="1079319" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Celeberrimo atque Illustrissimo Viro
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>P.</abbr><expan>Petrus</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>A.</abbr><expan>Antonius</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Mich.<hi rendition="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs></expan></choice> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p>Pergrat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi fuerunt tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="B_1722-08-12_991170515149205501" type="letter">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti, vom 12. August 1722</note>, quas die XII<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Augusti <rs key="place_GEO-2991214" type="place">Mu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lhusii</rs> ad me dedisti, et ex quibus intellexi Te potandar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>aquarum <rs key="place_GEO-2659224" type="place">Fabariensium</rs> causa illud oppidum petivisse.
             <lb/>Utinam illiusmodi aquarum auxilio ex tam longo, molesto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lque morbo evadas, atque ad pristin<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> redactus valetu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ldin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> negotiis tam publicis quam privatis operam pos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lsis dare. Rheumatismo, aut Arthridi Te conflictari s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lpe solere, ab <choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filio Tuo Nicolao</rs> non semel audi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lvi; cui morbo vel <choice><abbr>Illus.<hi rendition="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimus</expan></choice> atque <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rendition="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Laurentius Theu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lpolus</rs> h<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c Legatus pro Celsissima <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Republica</rs>
<lb/>est obnoxius, quinimo illo eodem morbo in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia
             <lb/>ille ipse nobilissimus Vir maximopere
             <lb/>torquetur. Lactis potu, seu di<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ta (uti appellant) Lactea,
             <lb/>ad istiusmodi <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gritudin<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> genera curanda nihil
             <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantius inveniri posse reor, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim si tophi
             <lb/>nondum circa articulos concreti fuerint, si longo
             <lb/>tempore lac hauriatur, sique <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gri ambulare, aut equita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lre non recusent, et aqua dulci vini loco utantur. Ce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lterum me Tibi, Vir Illustrissime, valde obstrictum profi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lteor, gratiasque ago quammaximas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d hospitium, et
             <lb/>mens<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> tuam, quando lares vestros accederem, generosiss<unclear>i</unclear><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lme mihi obtuleris. Mehercle Te salutare, Te videre, seu
             <lb/>de vultu cognoscere etiam atque etiam aveo; ac propte<pb facs="1079320" n="2"/>rea id efficere conabor, ut <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> Te salutandi, grati<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>que mei animi Tibi testificandi causa, pertranseam
             <lb/>in meo reditu, qui (quemadmod<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> spero) continget sub
             <lb/>Novembris initium, aut saltem dimidium. Si id facere
             <lb/>potero, agemus oretenus de illis rebus, de quibus longissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ma mea <rs key="B_1722-01-23_991170515149605501" type="letter">epistola</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, vom 23. Januar 1722</note>, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito jam mense Januario ad Te scripta,
             <lb/>verba feci. Interim etiam Tibi gratias ago, propterea quod binas
             <lb/>meas difficultates optime sustuleris ope rationis, qua
             <lb/>Fluida, anim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> gravitate abstrahendo, premunt corpora
             <lb/>circumstantia.</p>
<p><choice><abbr>Ingeniosiss.<hi rendition="#sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>Ingeniosissimam</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filii Tui Danielis</rs> <rs key="biblio_KGZSMV2E" type="biblio">de Respiratione</rs>
<lb/>Dissertation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ab <choice><abbr>Celeber.</abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119062372" type="person">Varignono</rs> mihi dono datam
         <lb/>nuper perlegi, eamque cedro dignam<note type="editorial">"cedro dignam" = "der Unsterblichkeit wert".</note> inveni, imo vero
         <lb/>ex illa ipsa Dissertatione ingenii eiusd<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filii Tui</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>s<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tantissimi magnitudinem statim cognovi. Quin
         <lb/>ille <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> me salutatum aliquando venturus
         <lb/>sit, nullus dubito; quo tempore me<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ei offero hospitium,
         <lb/>meam Bibliothecam, omniaque ad medic<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> praxim spec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tantia. Ut ipsi, et Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissimo alteri Filio <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolao</rs>, meo
         <lb/>nomine salut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> plurimam dicas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, et rogo.
             <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117584363" type="person">Laurentii Bellini</rs> <rs key="biblio_5ZHARN4Q" type="biblio">opuscula</rs><note type="editorial">Bellini, Lorenzo, Opera omnia, 2 vols, Venetiis (M. Hertz) 1708. (Titelblatt bei wellcome images). Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Jacob Hermann und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> pervolvendo incidi in hu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>iusmodi problema medicum, cujus solutionem (si vale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tudo tua, negotiaque permittent) ut ad me mittas
         <pb facs="1079321" n="3"/>
<lb/>maximopere precor. Quum enim scienti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> rerum,
         <lb/>sanguinis detraction<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> per arterias, aut venas, conse<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>quentium aggredi mihi sit in animo, eamque publici
         <lb/>juris facere, magn<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi erit utilitati hujusmodi pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>blematis solutio, quam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te major<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> in mod<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> peto.
         <lb/>"Dato maximo tempore, quo quis in naturali statu sine alimenti
         <lb/>sumptione vivere potest, invenire maximam quantitatem san<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>guinis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in statu similiter naturali mitti potest sine l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sione
         <lb/>virium: vel data maxima quantitate perspirationis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in
         <lb/>naturali statu singulis diebus fit, eandem maximam quan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>titatem mittendi sanguinis invenire: vel eandem repe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rire, data maxima consumptione sanguinis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> natura<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>liter se habente corpore, fit diebus singulis per operationes."</p>
<p>Vir <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rendition="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118639056" type="person">Fontenellius</rs>, qui Scienti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> de Infinito
         <lb/>nunc scribit ut Tibi salutem plurimam suo nomine
         <lb/>dicam mihi jubet. Id<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> facit <choice><abbr>Ingeniosiss.<hi rendition="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Ingeniosissimus</expan></choice> meique Amicissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mus Varignonius.</p> <closer><salute>Vale, Vir Amicissime, meque assiduo
            <lb/>pulcherrimar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tuarum litterarum commercio erudire,
            <lb/>atque ornare perge.</salute> <dateline>Dabam Luteti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiorum</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice><date when="1722-09-02"> 2. <choice><abbr>Septembr.</abbr><expan>Septembris</expan></choice> 1722.</date></dateline></closer>
